title: 300:  300th Episode Extravaganza!
description: Mind Pump's first episode went live January 5th, 2015. In less than a year and a half 300 episodes have been released. In this episode Sal, Adam & Justin talk about the Mind Pump philosophy and go behind the scenes about what drives the show and the mission. Get the Mind Pump Discount Red, Green & Black Super Bundle at www.mindpumpmedia.com Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Each week the best reviewers are announced on the show and sent Mind Pump T-shirts! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpmedia.com.
